      • solveAll

        public void solveAll(DEAProblem deaP)
              throws MissingDataException,
                     DEASolverException,
                     ProblemNotSolvedProperlyException
        This is the method that is called to solve a DEA Problem. This method only loops through the DMUs. Most sub-classes would inherit this method (as they extend the Model class) although some sub-classes might override this solve method. For example, the SBMI creates the constraint in the solve method as it is the same for all the problems regardless of the DMU under examination (it thus more computer efficient to override this solve method).
        Parameters:
        deaP - an instance of a DEAProblem
        Throws:
        MissingDataException
        DEASolverException
        ProblemNotSolvedProperlyException

      • createAndSolve

        public void createAndSolve(DEAProblem deaP,
                  int nbDMUs,
                  int nbVariables,
                  double[][] transposedMatrix,
                  DEAPSolution returnSol,
                  java.lang.Integer dmuIndex)
                    throws ProblemNotSolvedProperlyException,
                           DEASolverException,
                           MissingDataException
        this method is really just a signature mask for the createAndSolve methods. It is added here so that the solve method could call it. It should ALWAYS be overridden in the sub-classes extending this class. The code in the sub-classes methods overriding this createAndSolve method will solve a single DEA Problem for a specific DMUs.
        Parameters:
        deaP - an instance of a DEAProblem
        nbDMUs - the number of DMUs in deaP
        nbVariables - the number of variables in deaP
        transposedMatrix - the transposed matrix
        returnSol - the returned solution. This is a DEAPSolution in which all the solution is stored.
        dmuIndex - the index of the DMU under examination
        Throws:
        ProblemNotSolvedProperlyException
        DEASolverException
        MissingDataException
